                <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-8">
                    មិនទាន់មានគណនីមែនទេ?
                    <a href="http://127.0.0.1:8000/register" class="font-bold text-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-700 ml-1">
